"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The news of Quillâ€™s acquisition is bittersweet for me. On the one hand, I am over the moon for my friend, Ludwig Pettersson. On the other hand, I am sad to lose a tool that I love.\\n\\nQuill was the most thoughtful approach to online communication I have ever seen. It built on the innovations of Slack, Skype, Discord & Zoom in a wonderful way. It moved us forward.\\n\\nThe community I work with isâ€”quite franklyâ€”devastated at its loss. Hereâ€™s why:\\n\\n### Conversational Flow\\n\\nThe way conversations flowed on Quill *felt better* than Slack or Discord. It was like I could access more complicated thoughts because of the threading and grouping.\\n\\nActivity tab was a game changer: it summarised everything I needed to read.\\n\\n![Logging into Quill made my eyes feel rested](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/iDNYlEr1LwDjKgtNrBP5N.jpg?height=2048&width=1860)\\n\\n### Useful Notifications Instead Of Irritating Interruptions\\n\\nSlackâ€™s repetitive notification sound sends shivers down my spine. Quillâ€™s was infrequent and powerfulâ€”it meant something to me. I wanted to check it and always found something important.\\n\\n![A humane approach to digital communication](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/XMGpiQC_ortP-stCXE7Kw.jpg?height=2048&width=1860)\\n\\n### Natural Language Summaries\\n\\nLudwigâ€™s time at [OpenAI](https://openai.com/) was on full display in the product. Quill used their technology to intelligently summarise and title conversations to great effect. A magical touch âœ¨\\n\\n![The right way to share among the right people](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/dGw2w1dyLXuVPcI84XpvQ.jpg?height=2048&width=1860)\\n\\n### Obsessional About Attention\\n\\nQuill was not trying to get your attention; it was trying to give it back to you. Every single feature was designed to help you learn, discuss, decide and then get back to work.\\n\\n![I discovered a new feature almost every day I used it](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4NHE9RqkMhWH_QazNELPp.jpg?height=2048&width=1860)\\n\\n### Absolutely Beautiful\\n\\nGo to [their website](https://quill.chat/) and drink it in before it is removed forever. Just look at the incredible quality of the product design, copywriting and application presentation.\\n\\n![All the modes from my darkest to my brightest](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5cOb8NXhMi9ti1LjkuNdx.jpg?height=2048&width=1860)\\n\\n### Incredibly Powerful\\n\\nThe shear volume of features present across web, macOS, iOS & Android applications was stunning. The team were clearly firing on all cylinders creatively.\\n\\n![The opposite of feature creep](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/QqdbPaLyCsLpPBhDZtCCB.jpg?height=2048&width=1860)\\n\\n### Multi-Modal Connection \\n\\nSliding from text-based chat into voice-based discussion or video-based debate was easy. Quill blended the best modern web technologies together to make communication clearer.\\n\\n![Express yourself through your mode](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/GG5cQJOhJpP3LKMzco1y7.jpg?height=2048&width=1860)\\n\\n### Thank you, Quill\\n\\nThe team behind this software touched my heart and helped my community get started. I will always be grateful to them.\\n\\n![Thank you](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/6cSUHl33_loZ-yu4p9Ck2.png?height=388&width=1394)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1639535328,\"title\":\"Why We Will Miss Quill ðŸª¶\",\"publication\":\"ricburton\"},\"digest\":\"umBG0aVgOavWxL2cFf89QrkdrQ2Mcq7msWUoxQZnO-U\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x225E9B54F41F44F42150b6aAA730Da5f2d23FAf2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cZOs3mn6pxc7L_S_swV_EZsp5B76-ESwKc5aR12eeOo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"VxWAOwZ2iBkgW1A_jy431WSAeDlzZ204JIdxsKslDLM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"FmFpdyhXDRgt0FizoNwM0WjFNFtG7-CyY8NMGlAoCEJtI_Lap7Qlqfs-TI-vobRWapdmy0iB4eS_analxM7gag\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3ff7568448bea558cd6e34f8dd727cea8297c42c7bf3cbb774659a9c61125308198a7225deced4427934c54fedbcfdea94ceb821d9503670df51a3c91727fb2d1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cZOs3mn6pxc7L_S_swV_EZsp5B76-ESwKc5aR12eeOo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"VxWAOwZ2iBkgW1A_jy431WSAeDlzZ204JIdxsKslDLM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"umBG0aVgOavWxL2cFf89QrkdrQ2Mcq7msWUoxQZnO-U\"}"